{"tid":1535953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重 中共可能做緊野 5毛國際化 YouTube化","createTime":"2019-09-03T14:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T10:41:55.000Z","uid":181141,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8f3565eab311702028cb27fb102f45fab1e4aba7","tid":1535953,"uid":181141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:04:02.000Z","msg":"大家有冇發現 fb多左好多非支那人5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地幾乎所有都來自馬來西亞 新加坡<br />\n其實我地香港事點解佢地咁關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地好撐香港黑警 成日叫佢地捉哂示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要特登入去蘋果 立場 去留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好奇怪 正如我哋都唔會特登去馬來西亞d page留言啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多外國YouTube d comment都話我地好暴力 撐黑警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下面cap左圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要屈我地拎錘仔打個阿伯<br />\n但我我睇關於烏克蘭嘅YouTube都唔會話示威者暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟發生咩事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqXOh3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqXOh3w.png&h=a9f04b43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09f2a0f91f35ccea6b3f955046e63cfce3901cf0","tid":1535953,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T14:04:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img